{"tid":2207764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上水遊行險墮橋科大男生　認藏生果刀天拿水　還押侯判","createTime":"2020-09-18T11:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T12:30:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ba01053afaf48f7b7dac5b627b8de8802c178ff7","tid":2207764,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"去年 7 月於上水遊行中險墮橋的科大男學生，被指今年 1 月 5 日在「上水和理行」遊行後管有生果刀、扳手、木棍等；及於 5 月 27 日反國安法遊行前，在銅鑼灣管有天拿水及鎚仔等，分別被控管有攻擊性武器罪及管有物品意圖損壞財產罪。他今（18 日）於東區裁判法院承認兩罪，還押至下月 13 日索取背景報告後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告患有基因疾病，8 歲時診斷他有高功能自閉症及資優，但同時亦有專注力不足及社交障礙等問題，他近年更拒絕與外界溝通，甚至與父母亦沒有傾談。辯方又指被告欠缺自理及社交能力，如判囚對他影響甚大及難以適應，希望法庭可盡量考慮非監禁式刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E9%9A%AA%E5%A2%AE%E6%A9%8B%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F-%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E5%88%80%E5%A4%A9%E6%8B%BF%E6%B0%B4-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%BE%AF%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%258B%25BF%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25BE%25AF%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=7ef6025f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%258B%25BF%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25BE%25AF%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=741ce003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4